{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_10",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 10",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あーあ、今年は最後の学園祭か～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh man‚ this year will be the last school festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これが終わったら受験一色だぜ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After it’s over‚ we’ll be slammed with exams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For that reason!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最後に思いっきり盛り上がるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should enjoy this last event to the fullest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.4833333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.483333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～あ、出席日数不足で\nこのままだと卒業出来ないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ I haven’t attended school for enough days.\nI won’t be able to graduate at this rate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと計算してたはずなのに\nどうしてこんなことに……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I’d calculated everything correctly.\nHow did this happen?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈が計算外の仕事を\nいくつもやりたがるからだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because you always want to do work\nwhich is outside of your calculations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "えーっ、私のせい？\nスケジュール管理はマネージャーの仕事でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? So it’s my fault?\nIsn’t it the manager’s job to manage the schedule?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そのスケジュールをことごとく破壊されたら\nどうしようもないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you keep messing up the schedule like this‚\nthere's nothing I can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "担任",
      "speakerNameEn": "Class",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……何度数えても、やっぱり足りないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how many times I count‚ it's still not enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "担任",
      "speakerNameEn": "Class",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残念ながら、二人とも来年は高校四年生ということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unfortunately‚ both of you will be the 4th year high school students next year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは困ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That won’t do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "担任",
      "speakerNameEn": "Class",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "前向きに考えれば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you think about it positively‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "担任",
      "speakerNameEn": "Class",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "来年も現役高校生アイドルでいられるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you can be a high school student idol next year as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいやいや！　勘弁して下さいよ！\n留年アイドルなんて、なんの売りにもならないです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no no no! Please spare us!\nAn idol repeating a year? That won’t sell at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "先生、なんとかなりませんか！？\n私なんでもしますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ can’t you do something?!\nI’ll do anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当になんでも、ですか？　長瀬さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll really do anything‚ Nagase?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 68.36666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、校長先生……はい！\nなんでもです！　卒業出来るならなんでもします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Principal… Yes!\nAnything! So long as I can graduate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 72.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、麻奈\n気軽に女の子がなんでもするなんて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ Mana.\nA girl shouldn’t be agreeing to do anything so casually――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんと一緒に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both {user} and I will do anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺もセットなのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why am I a part of this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "担任",
      "speakerNameEn": "Class",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しかし、校長、二人とも出席日数がかなり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ Principal‚ both of their attendance rates are quite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、補習は受けてもらいます。ですが教育とは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they will take supplementary lessons‚ but education should be",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "生徒の個性を伸ばすため、柔軟であるべきですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "flexible in order to foster students’ individuality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "校長先生、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much‚ Principal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのかわりに一つだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ in return",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私のお願いを聞いてほしいのです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a single favor to ask!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "お、お願いってなんでしょうか……？\n{user}くんに一体何をやらせる気――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what is the favor?\nI wonder what in the world he’s going to make you do‚ {user}――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さらっと俺一人にかぶせないでくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t put all of this on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "校長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Principal",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、実は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ actually――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_10-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まさか学園祭でライブをやってくれなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never expected to perform a live at the school festival…",
