      "text": "校長先生のお孫さんが、私のファンだったなんてね\n……でも、おかげで助かっちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out the principal's grandchildren is a fan of mine.\n…But‚ it ended up being a lifesaver.",
        "id": ""
