      "text": "でも孫を喜ばせるために、生徒にライブやらせるなんて\n職権乱用じゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But isn’t getting a student to perform just to make his\ngrandchildren happy an abuse of his position?",
        "id": ""
