      "text": "固いこと言わない。ファンのために歌えて\nしかも！　卒業まで出来ちゃうんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't be so uptight. I got to sing for my fans‚ and on top of that‚\nwe can graduate‚ right?",
        "id": ""
